              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Property Search</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive market search with access to both on-market and off-market opportunities 
              to identify properties that match your specific operational requirements.
            </p>
