              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Due Diligence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Thorough property evaluation including zoning compliance, 
              environmental assessments, and infrastructure analysis to protect your interests.
            </p>
